<div class="border border-yellow-300 bg-yellow-200 rounded-lg p-8 mt-8">
  <div class=" text-center text-yellow-700">
    This demo uses fake stock data. To use it with real data, you need an API key from Alpha Vantage
    <a href="https://www.alphavantage.co/support/#api-key" class="text-blue-500">here.</a>
  </div>
  <div class=" text-center text-yellow-700">
    Once you have your key, add it to the Rails credentials file or use <code>VANTAGE_API_KEY</code> environment variable.
  </div>
  <div class="mt-4">
    <div class="font-mono bg-gray-100 p-0.5">$ rails credentials:edit</div>
    <div class="font-mono bg-gray-100 p-0.5 mt-2">
      <div>alpha_vantage:</div>
      <div class="ml-4">api_key: <span class="text-gray-500">&lt;YOUR KEY HERE&gt;</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="mt-8 w-full flex">
  <%= link_to 'Proceed with fake prices', tickers_path(proceed: true), class: "mx-auto inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-white bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-green-500" %>
</div>
